*1961. ''Hanged by the Neck''. Reuses some material from ''Reflections on Hanging''.
*1963. ''[[Suicide of a Nation]]''. 
*1964. ''[[The Act of Creation]]''.
*1967. ''[[The Ghost in the Machine]]''. Penquin reprint 1990: ISBN 0140191925.
