**[[Metagnostidae]]
**[[Peronopsidae]]
**[[Ptychagnostidae]]
*'''Superfamily&amp;nbsp;[[Condylopygoidea]]'''
**[[Condylopygidae]]
'''Suborder [[Eodiscina]]'''&lt;br /&gt;
*'''Superfamily&amp;nbsp;[[Eodiscoidea]]'''
